content:
A softphone is a customizable call-control tool that appears to users assigned to a call center. A softphone's functionality and user interface are determined by the Salesforce admin.

Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

IMPORTANT CTI Toolkit is retired and no longer supported. To continue using CTI functionality, migrate to Salesforce Open CTI.

Salesforce Call Center
Get to Know Your Softphone Features
Use a Softphone in the Salesforce Console in Salesforce Classic
title: Understanding Softphones
